Interface IPoyntReceiptPrintingService

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface IPoyntReceiptPrintingService
extends IInterface
    Provides the interfaces necessary to print receipts for an order or transaction or custom receipt.

      • printReceipt

        void printReceipt(String jobId,
                  PrintedReceipt receipt,
                  IPoyntReceiptPrintingServiceListener callback)
           throws RemoteException
        Print a receipt to the onboard printer representing an order. The order of the contents will be as follow: PrintedReceipt.headerImage (if provided) PrintedReceipt.header PrintedReceipt.body PrintedReceipt.footer PrintedReceipt.footerImage (if provided) The text header/body/footer can be any text content the client chooses. The optional headerImage and footerImage are byte arrays representing Bitmap image of the client's choosing.
        Parameters:
        jobId - client provided UUID for reference
        receipt - co.poynt.api.model.PrintedReceipt custom receipt content to be printed
        callback - IPoyntReceiptPrintingServiceListener
        Throws:
        RemoteException
